data.text:
Fiber Marine

Fiber Marine is a Shipping Management and Trading Co. who is a related company of Hayat Holding. Fiber Marine was established in 2016 in the maritime sector with purchasing MV Pine, then it has breathed with MV Acacia. Currently, MV Maple, new built vessel, was delivered to Fiber Marine on 25 July 2018.

The purpose of Fiber Marine is shipping, chartering and handling operations professionally. We’re investing in the future with the upcoming projects as Fiber Marine with our inspired, experienced and thriving company.
